{"tid":981882,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"ASSO仔自嘆確悽慘！","createTime":"2019-01-14T15:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T12:27:06.000Z","uid":52764,"like":7,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8e88f9c432a9a0e9c8ec5585bc62682451d0f2e2","tid":981882,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"ASSO仔自嘆確悽慘，成日抄SOURCE走堂時時慣，地方好似垃圾剷，見親戚梗會撞正板。<br />\n在這環境諸多顧忌，拉巴似生番，一日走左堂，直情有難，食頹飯有如食快餐，睇見都心冰冷！<br />\n人地上莊，夜夜嘈成晚，孤單怎過長夜漫？<br />\n<br />\nGROUPMATES交野零舍慢，LECTURER飛書無忌憚，<br />\n咁樣做人做到心都淡，啲FREE RIDER的確係野蠻！<br />\n認真慘！慘！慘！<br />\n唉屌GPA啱啱過二，你話有乜揀？一次報NONJU搞到我唔夠錢吔飯！<br />\n讀書越嚟越困難，出黎做野人又懶，嘆孤單！"},{"pid":"4ea54702b2f349b8771fb244bfdb9752ddad9e83","tid":981882,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f33ec8f91374ba15e4b4863c45205487695663a","tid":981882,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"咩歌黎"},{"pid":"172edd47b136ac4694b603374fca126ed5323ab5","tid":981882,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f33ec8f91374ba15e4b4863c45205487695663a","tid":981882,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"咩歌黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"分飛燕"},{"pid":"3de65a48fee206cf860a8e41998bb011f75c936a","tid":981882,"uid":175598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6c353d85b1838dbf9d6d02c8cc62a6ea67a6cf1","tid":981882,"uid":52068,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"4.3/10<br />\n比你爆4啦"},{"pid":"76c7f01986fa6b6575128074f21c33111f764edb","tid":981882,"uid":191155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T18:44:35.000Z","msg":"高登李清照"},{"p